              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33362761/" class="">重版序言2</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/97399948/" class=" " title="卓兰">卓兰</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33362761">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">欲洞察真相求取真知，坚守“独立之精神，自由之思想”是第一要务。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-11-08 16:31</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                欲洞察真相求取真知，坚守“独立之精神，自由之思想”是第一要务。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
